{"tid":2213532,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"課程檢討報告︱教育局審查傳媒 只邀大公文匯星島明報採訪","createTime":"2020-09-22T14:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T15:22:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a77bff838198b64e9df672d8e1fd834a7f78d13d","tid":2213532,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"學校課程檢討專責小組今日向教育局提交報告，提出多項有關通識科的富爭議性建議，惟教育局一改以往安排記者會解釋專責小組報告慣例，僅以新聞稿形式交代和上載報告至教育局網頁，未有召開記者會。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》獲悉，教育局破天荒只安排《大公報》、《文匯報》、《星島日報》和《明報》作「小圍」採訪，由主席陳黃麗娟「導讀」。有議員炮轟教局審查傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/5PKEUDCWCBDRXJWEGSLW2KD6JE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F5PKEUDCWCBDRXJWEGSLW2KD6JE%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I29g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=eb9f6bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F5PKEUDCWCBDRXJWEGSLW2KD6JE%2F&h=f7f7088d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/5PKEUDCWCBDRXJWEGSLW2KD6JE/</a>"},{"pid":"493cc17690989b82ff6525535cd362b12f255d77","tid":2213532,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4160a90cebfd6a00c8f2a3fa6f9c71eab2222bf","tid":2213532,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"笑撚柒死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4a99e43b3c8edcc1a8e6cc4459866b5845b6e2","tid":2213532,"uid":324629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"493cc17690989b82ff6525535cd362b12f255d77","tid":2213532,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5648c6feb75a8dc3b5e180bb9f8dfb2f0803df0c","tid":2213532